```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  participant App as AppService
  participant SDK as FlagSDK (in-process)
  participant MGMT as ManagementAPI
  participant Redis as Redis

  Note over App,Redis: Startup — seed local cache
  App->>SDK: initialize()
  SDK->>MGMT: GET /flags (all flags)
  MGMT->>Redis: HGETALL flags
  Redis-->>MGMT: flag definitions
  MGMT-->>SDK: flag payload
  SDK->>SDK: seed in-process cache
  SDK->>MGMT: open SSE /flags/stream
  MGMT-->>SDK: SSE connection established

  Note over App,Redis: Request — local evaluation (no network)
  App->>SDK: evaluate("checkout-v2", { userId, tenantId })
  SDK->>SDK: look up flag in local cache
  SDK->>SDK: evaluate targeting rules in priority order
  SDK-->>App: { variant: "enabled", ruleMatched: "percentage-10" }

  Note over App,Redis: Background — flag update pushed
  MGMT->>Redis: SET flag:checkout-v2 { percentage: 50 }
  MGMT->>Redis: APPEND audit_log entry
  MGMT-->>SDK: SSE event: flag:checkout-v2 updated
  SDK->>SDK: update in-process cache entry

  Note over App,Redis: Kill switch — on-call disables flag
  App->>MGMT: PUT /flags/new-search-algorithm { defaultValue: false }
  MGMT->>Redis: SET flag:new-search-algorithm { defaultValue: false }
  MGMT-->>SDK: SSE event: flag:new-search-algorithm updated
  SDK->>SDK: cache updated — all subsequent evaluations return false
```
